{
  "stem": "1721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then-- I don't remember the sequence of the events after that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was separated from my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was put into a children's compound within the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My head was shaven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The children's compound-- I-- I never did understand why they separated us out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I guess probably for expeditiously-- that way they could control the parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Maybe the parents wouldn't try any funny business if their children were separated from them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I don't know how many children were there at-- at one time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But it was a separate barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there could've been 50, 60, 75 children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They are just faces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't remember any one in particular.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't think I recall any one or two children that I knew for any length of time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I think they just sort of came and went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that's basically where we were housed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I was supposed to see her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I mean, you know, they made it a point for me to visit with my mother once a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Of whatever time I saw her, I think they were really kind of uneventful.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't recall them being very loving or emotional.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I think it was just sort of duty bound.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I didn't really see her very often while we were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in that sense, yeah, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will agree that in retrospect, we were very lucky to have been in that camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- I don't really know what the-- what the goals were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I never did find out what they had in mind for us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
